# OpenAI Rate Limits

OpenAI rate limits are enforced per-organization at the model level. Understanding and handling them is critical for production applications.

## Rate Limit Types

| Limit Type | Abbreviation | Description |
|------------|-------------|-------------|
| Requests per minute | RPM | Maximum API calls per minute |
| Tokens per minute | TPM | Maximum input + output tokens per minute |
| Requests per day | RPD | Maximum API calls per day |
| Tokens per day | TPD | Maximum tokens per day (some tiers) |
| Images per minute | IPM | For image generation endpoints |

